Yvonne Levy Kushner https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yvonne_Levy_Kushner 0 Yvonne Kushner (née Levy; October 12, 1906 – February 8, 1990) was an American actress and socialite in New York and Washington, DC. She became a philanthropist for women's health and Jewish causes.
